{"word":"καταμαρτυρέω","slug":"καταμαρτυρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταμαρτυρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to bear witness against</i>, <el>τινός</el> or <el>κατά τινος</el> <b>Oratt.</b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> et <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>καταμαρτυροῦσιν αὐτὸν λαβεῖν</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to have evidence given against</i> one, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> also of the evidence, <i>to be given against</i> one, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}